OL,3,CCrews tackle multiple wildfires across
OL,4,CWales as public urged to be vigilant
OL,6,FEmergency services have urged the
OL,7,Fpublic to be vigilant as they deal
OL,8,Fwith multiple wildfires across Wales
OL,9,Fthat have been burning for several
OL,10,Fdays.
OL,12,FFirefighters have entered the third
OL,13,Fday of battling a "large" wildfire in
OL,14,FBannau Brycheiniog National Park while
OL,15,Fother fires in the Elan Valley area
OL,16,Fhave been burning since Sunday (26
OL,17,FApril).
