OL,3,CCrews tackle multiple wildfires across
OL,4,CWales as public urged to be vigilant
OL,6,FSouth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,7,Fsaid the fire in Bannau Brycheiniog
OL,8,FNational Park first started on the
OL,9,Fafternoon of 29 April and the blaze
OL,10,Fhas affected an area of around 20
OL,11,Fsquare kilometres.
OL,13,FThe fire has impacted forests, peat,
OL,14,Fand grassland, which the service said
OL,15,Fis leading to challenging conditions
OL,16,Ffor crews. Multiple appliances were
OL,17,Fsent to tackle the blaze, including
OL,18,Fall terrain vehicles and drones.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
