OL,3,CCrews tackle multiple wildfires across
OL,4,CWales as public urged to be vigilant
OL,6,FThe fire service said it is working
OL,7,Fwith the National Trust, Natural
OL,8,FResources Wales and South Wales Police.
OL,10,FMeanwhile, Mid and West Wales Fire and
OL,11,FRescue Service have entered the fifth
OL,12,Fday of tackling several wildfires in
OL,13,Fthe Elan Valley area.
OL,15,FTargeted water helicopter water drops
OL,16,Fhave been used to suppress fires in
OL,17,Fdifficult to access areas.
OL,19,FThe fires in Elan valley are in areas
OL,20,Fwhich support vulnerable nesting
OL,21,Fbirds, small mammals and rare plants.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
